---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { getRelativeLocaleUrl } from "astro:i18n";
---

<BaseLayout
  lang="en"
  title="Initiators | Digital Independence Day"
  description="About the initiators of Digital Independence Day"
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-4xl">
    <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <h1>Initiators</h1>

      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8">
        Digital Independence Day is an initiative for digital self-determination
        and privacy.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        We want to support people in achieving digital independence. Every first
        Sunday of the month, we encourage everyone to take a step toward
        privacy-friendly and ethical digital services.
      </p>

      <h2>Why Digital Independence Day?</h2>
      <p>
        Big tech corporations collect massive amounts of data, influence our
        perception through algorithms, and have an enormous impact on our lives.
        However, there are privacy-friendly and ethical alternatives for almost
        every service.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Values</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Privacy</strong>: Your data belongs to you</li>
        <li><strong>Transparency</strong>: Open systems and open source</li>
        <li>
          <strong>Independence</strong>: No dependency on big corporations
        </li>
        <li><strong>Community</strong>: Together we are stronger</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Get Involved</h2>
      <p>
        DI.DAY lives from the community. You can contribute in various ways:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Share your experiences with alternatives</li>
        <li>Help others switch</li>
        <li>Organize local events on the first Sunday</li>
        <li>Create your own recipes</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Supporters & Partners</h2>
      <p>
        Digital Independence Day is supported by various organizations and
        individuals dedicated to digital rights, privacy, and open source.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-primary-50 dark:bg-primary-950 rounded-xl">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Contact</h3>
        <p>
          Do you have questions or want to get involved?<br />
          <a
            href={getRelativeLocaleUrl("en", "newsletter")}
            class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 hover:underline"
          >
            Subscribe to our newsletter
          </a> or contact us directly.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .prose :global(h1) {
    @apply text-4xl font-display font-bold mb-8 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100;
  }

  .prose :global(h2) {
    @apply text-2xl font-display font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100;
  }

  .prose :global(h3) {
    @apply text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100;
  }

  .prose :global(p) {
    @apply mb-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300;
  }

  .prose :global(ul) {
    @apply list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-4;
  }

  .prose :global(li) {
    @apply text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300;
  }

  .prose :global(a) {
    @apply text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 hover:underline;
  }
</style>
